    <updated>2015-08-12T15:56:28+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://andylinid45.github.io/blog/2015/08/12/how-to-learn-fast</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>看官方的英文文档，看中文文档是一个坑
</span><span class='line'>用英文搜索问题而不是中文，多看stackoverflow.com ，里面的回答都很好
</span><span class='line'>看用到的开源库的源代码。所有东西都在源代码里，有问题就debug进去
</span><span class='line'>精读技术书籍是坑，要快速浏览大概。书本不能帮你解决具体技术问题
</span><span class='line'>要学以致用，切忌天马行空、纸上谈兵
</span><span class='line'>多写demo</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
